cab.content: /BATTLE SITUATION * UOON - 23rd WAY, 19IB,- f1, Considerable gas shelling by the enemy took place north and east of BETHUNE, and east of HAZEBROUCK,2:* This morning there is no change in the general situation, and nothing of interest to report *General Staff,War Office, S.W.I. 23rd May, 1918* Issued at 11-45 a,m*
